{"article_id":"ABjaOAGxXGbupLv7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"There is one mystery left to solve","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"before the Supreme Court gathers","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to hear a challenge to Proposition 8 in late March .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"That is :","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Will the Department of Justice weigh in on the case in favor of opponents of Prop 8 , the California ballot measure","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that defined marriage as between one man and one woman ?","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"And what will it say ?","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Hollingsworth v. Perry concerns the California ballot initiative ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"enacted in 2008 .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"In a brief","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"filed with the court on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"opponents of Prop 8 made broad arguments","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"claiming","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that it is unconstitutional .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"`` Proposition 8 is an arbitrary , irrational and discriminatory measure","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that denies gay men and lesbians their fundamental right","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to marry","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"in violation of the due process and equal protection clauses , ''","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"the opponents said .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The brief was written by Theodore B. Olson and David Boies ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"who represent the American Foundation for Equal Rights .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"They wrote ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` Because of their sexual orientation","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"-- a characteristic","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"with which they were born","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"and which they can not change --","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"plaintiffs and hundreds of thousands of gay men and lesbians in California and across the country are being excluded from one of life 's most precious relationships .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"`` They may not marry the person","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"they love ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"the person","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"with whom they wish to partner","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"in building a family","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"and with whom they wish to share their future and their most intimate and private dreams , ''","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"they added .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"The arguments tackled more than just the ruling","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that struck down Prop 8 on narrow grounds specific to California 's history on the issue of gay marriage .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"The language was sweeping :","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"`` The only substantive question in this case is whether the state is entitled to exclude gay men and lesbians from the institution of marriage","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and deprive their relationships","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"-- their love --","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"of the respect , and dignity and social acceptance ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that heterosexual marriages enjoy . `","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"` This badge of inferiority , separateness and inequality must be extinguished .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"When it is ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"America will be closer to fulfilling the aspirations of its citizens , ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"they wrote .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"A month ago , supporters of Prop 8 filed their brief in the case .","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"Read it HERE .","depth":3},{"id":48,"text":"While the administration will certainly weigh in on the other gay marriage case in front of the court","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"-- a challenge to the federal law , the Defense of Marriage Act","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"( DOMA ) --","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"it has never filed a brief in the Prop 8 case","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"because it was not directly involved .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"While the DOMA case challenges a federal law","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"that denies federal benefits to same-sex couples","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"who are legally married in their state ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"the Prop 8 case asks a much broader question :","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"Is there a fundamental right to gay marriage under the Constitution .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Solicitor General Donald B. Verrilli Jr. is not required to file a so-called `` friend of the court '' brief in the Prop 8 case ,","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"but sources said","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"the administration is considering the possibility at the highest levels .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"If it chooses to weigh in ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"it has to do so by the last week of February .","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"In San Francisco Wednesday , President Obama told station KGO-TV ,","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"`` The solicitor general is still looking at this .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"I have to make sure","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"I 'm not interjecting myself too much into this process ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"particularly when we 're not party to the case .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"I can tell you , though ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that obviously my personal view is that I think","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that same-sex couples should have the same rights","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and be treated like everybody else . ''","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"At the White House briefing on Thursday , White House spokesman Jay Carney said ,","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"you have seen no expression from the president on the constitutional or legal aspects of this .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"He has an opinion , obviously , about Proposition 8 as policy ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"but we have no comment and nothing","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to say at this point","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"about an issue","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that is properly looked at as a legal and constitutional matter over at the Department of Justice . ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Back in May , the president told ' Robin Roberts","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that he had evolved on the issue of gay marriage","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"and had come to personally support it .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"He seemed to suggest in the interview , however ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"that he felt","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"the issue should be left up to the states .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"`` I continue to believe","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that this is an issue","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"that is going to be worked out at the local level","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"because , historically , this has not been a federal issue , what 's recognized as marriage , ''","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"the president said .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"But at the inauguration , he used much broader language :","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"'' Our journey is not complete","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"until our gay brothers and sisters are treated like anyone else under the law","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"-- for","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"if we are truly created equal ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"then surely the love","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"we commit to one another","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"must be equal , as well . ''","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Even if the Department of Justice files a brief ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"it does n't have to get to the broad question .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"It could , for example , limit its arguments to whether the supporters of Prop 8","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"-- in the absence of California officials","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"who have refused to defend it --","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"have a legal right","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"to bring the case .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Or , it could argue in favor of the relatively narrow opinion from the 9th Circuit Court of Appeals .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"In a conference call on Thursday , Olson urged the administration to step in .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"`` We very much would like the United States , in the form of the solicitor general , to file a brief , ''","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Olson ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"who served as the solicitor general under the George W. Bush administration ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"added","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that the justices pay particular attention","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"when briefs come in on behalf of the government .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":162,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":160,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":123,"right":159,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":121,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":117,"right":120,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":116,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":3,"right":118,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":147,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":127,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p